I don't know about Seong Hyeon Group, but the SH Mall shares belong to my late father.

492
00:39:08,300 --> 00:39:12,800
That's right up to now. In the future, it'll be up to how you act.

493
00:39:12,800 --> 00:39:14,500
Don't blackmail me pointlessly.

494
00:39:14,500 --> 00:39:17,199
You're giving your shares to some woman

495
00:39:17,199 --> 00:39:18,299
as a way to get me to come back to the company.

496
00:39:18,299 --> 00:39:19,299
What's the meaning of this?

497
00:39:19,299 --> 00:39:22,900
What do you mean, blackmail? How could you say that to your grandpa?

498
00:39:22,900 --> 00:39:25,000
If Da Hyeon knew you'd be this uncouth,

499
00:39:25,000 --> 00:39:27,299
I'm sure she'd be quite disappointed.

500
00:39:27,299 --> 00:39:29,200
Why don't you marry her yourself, then?

501
00:39:29,200 --> 00:39:31,800
I know, right? If only I were 30 years younger...

502
00:39:31,800 --> 00:39:32,800
Geez.

503
00:39:32,800 --> 00:39:36,700
You make the decision. I'm not trying to sell you anything, here.

504
00:39:36,700 --> 00:39:39,600
No, you're doing exactly that.

505
00:39:39,600 --> 00:39:42,599
Ju Hee from last time was Chairman Han's daughter.

506
00:39:42,599 --> 00:39:44,799
It would've been perfect to have their company merge with Seong Hyeon Chemicals.

507
00:39:44,799 --> 00:39:46,399
And yet, you refused!

508
00:39:46,399 --> 00:39:48,599
If you'd just gotten married back then,

509
00:39:48,599 --> 00:39:50,899
Seong Hyeon Chemicals would've been much more profitable.

510
00:39:50,899 --> 00:39:54,300
We could've even dominated the bio industry first as well.

511
00:39:54,300 --> 00:39:56,899
It seems like you need to sell your grandson off in marriage

512
00:39:56,899 --> 00:40:01,200
to keep Seong Hyeon Chemicals afloat, but I don't do business like that.

513
00:40:01,200 --> 00:40:04,800
What is it about that teacher that you're investing so much in her?

514
00:40:04,800 --> 00:40:10,200
She's a special child. She has something that neither of us has.

515
00:40:10,200 --> 00:40:14,600
I don't know what that may be. But what if I refuse?

516
00:40:14,600 --> 00:40:16,099
Jae In.

517
00:40:16,099 --> 00:40:22,399
Well, Seong Hyeon Group will become Tae Ha's. Of course, that includes SH Mall's shares.

518
00:40:22,399 --> 00:40:24,700
There's no reason that you must be my successor, after all.

519
00:40:26,000 --> 00:40:30,700
Actually, I called Tae Ha over. I want to hear what he has to say.

520
00:40:44,000 --> 00:40:45,800
Oh yeah.

521
00:40:58,600 --> 00:41:00,900
These scammers aren't calling me anymore.

522
00:41:00,900 --> 00:41:03,899
It'd be nice if he really was the grandson of Seong Hyeon Group's chairman.

523
00:41:03,899 --> 00:41:08,000
That way, he could make Ji Su their main model and help him out.

524
00:41:12,699 --> 00:41:16,800
Did you call me and Tae Ha over to try and compare us?

525
00:41:20,000 --> 00:41:24,500
Fine. You've managed to find my weakness.

526
00:41:24,500 --> 00:41:28,500
But I'm not nice enough to just sit and take your bait.

527
00:41:28,500 --> 00:41:32,200
Therefore, let's take this opportunity to negotiate things.

528
00:41:32,200 --> 00:41:33,800
You're really going to marry her?

529
00:41:33,800 --> 00:41:36,400
Hell no!

530
00:41:36,400 --> 00:41:38,400
Like I said, I'm not a nice person.

531
00:41:38,400 --> 00:41:41,199
As if I didn't know that already. So?

532
00:41:41,199 --> 00:41:43,900
I'll date her, at the very least.

533
00:41:43,900 --> 00:41:47,300
I'll seriously date her for just three months.

534
00:41:47,300 --> 00:41:49,300
And if it doesn't work out, I'll chalk it up to fate.

535
00:41:49,300 --> 00:41:51,199
And you must give up.

536
00:41:51,199 --> 00:41:52,600
One year.

537
00:41:54,800 --> 00:41:56,900
Five months.

538
00:41:56,900 --> 00:41:58,600
Six months.

539
00:42:22,799 --> 00:42:25,699
My grandpa wants us to get married.

540
00:42:25,699 --> 00:42:27,300
She wants all three of us to meet up.

541
00:42:27,300 --> 00:42:29,500
And why do I need to agree to that?

542
00:42:29,500 --> 00:42:30,500
Who else would she want to see, then, if not you?

543
00:42:30,500 --> 00:42:32,200
She says that she really doesn't know who you are!

544
00:42:32,200 --> 00:42:37,100
Well, you take care of that. That's your mission.

545
00:42:37,100 --> 00:42:38,899
Want me to carry you in?

546
00:42:41,000 --> 00:42:44,300
Do you know what a three-legged race is?

547
00:42:44,300 --> 00:42:48,200
My grandpa has tied you and me together.

548
00:42:48,200 --> 00:42:51,400
- With what?
- Marriage.

549
00:42:51,400 --> 00:42:53,290
[One Percent of Something]
